<center><h2>Registration</h2></center>
<ol>
<li class="normal">  There will be no registration fees for authors with accepted papers, but registration is necessary for the effectiveness and good organization of the event program. After the author(s) receives the acceptance notification email, a registration form must be filled out and send back to the conference secretariat. This free registration includes one copy of the Zanco Transaction Journal, conference documents and stationary, coffee breaks, lunch, dinner, welcome reception, closing, and banquet ticket.</li>
<li class="normal">  Researchers, academics, and industry representatives without papers are welcome to participate, and in this case as well, registration is necessary. There will be a $50 US registration fee applied. The registration form must be filled out and sent before the due date, but the fee may be paid at the registration desk during the conference. This registration includes one copy of the Zanco Transaction Journal, conference documents and stationary, coffee breaks, lunch, dinner, welcome reception, closing, and banquet ticket.</li>
</ol>
<div style="padding:20px 20px 20px 20px">
